# grandMA2 FX Buttons Macro Commands

## Macros for FX Buttons

### Strobe Hit
Command: `Exec "Strobe Hit"`

### Blinder Hit
Command: `Exec "Blinder Hit"`

### Audience Sweep
Command: `Exec "Audience Sweep"`

### Strobe Chase
Command: `Exec "Strobe Chase"`

### Big White Hit
Command: `Exec "Big White Hit"`

### Blackout
Command: `Exec "Blackout"`